title: Fruit Stab Challenge
description: Fruit Stab Challenge is an ultimate knife-throwing game where you must prove your accuracy skills. Precision is key as you stab the fruits. Complete levels by hitting each fruit the required number of times, showcasing your quickness and precision. Unlock special knives to enhance your performance and climb the leaderboard. Brace yourself for a frenzy of fruity mayhem and see how far you can go in conquering levels. Get ready to unleash your inner fruit-stabbing champion and let the chaos unfold!
